{"word":"Syria","slug":"syria","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Syria</b> <a href=\"#/H758\">H758</a> <br/> Highlands lying between the river Euphrates and the Mediterranean Sea.<br/> Called Aram, from the son of Shem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=23'>Gen 10:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=23&verse=7'>Num 23:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=17'>1Ch 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=23'>1Ch 2:23</a><br/> In the time of Abraham it seems to have embraced the region between the rivers Tigris and Euphrates<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=10'>Gen 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=20'>Gen 25:20</a><br/> In the time of Abraham, it included Padan-Aram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=20'>Gen 25:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=5'>Gen 28:5</a><br/> Minor kingdoms within the region:<br/> - Aramzobah, called also Zobah and Zoba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=47'>1Sa 14:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=3'>2Sa 8:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=6'>2Sa 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=8'>2Sa 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=23'>1Ki 11:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=5'>1Ch 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=9'>1Ch 18:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=19&verse=6'>1Ch 19:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=1'>Psa 60:1</a> <br/> - Geshur<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=8'>2Sa 15:8</a> <br/> - Aram-rehob, called also Beth-Rehob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=6'>2Sa 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=8'>2Sa 10:8</a> <br/> - Damascus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=6'>2Sa 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=6'>1Ch 18:6</a> <br/> - Hamath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=10'>2Sa 8:10</a> <br/> Conquest of:<br/> - Conquest of:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=13'>2Sa 8:13</a> <br/> - By Jeroboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Ki 14:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=28'>2Ki 14:28</a> <br/> - By Tiglath-Pileser, king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Ki 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=34'>2Ki 18:34</a> <br/> People of, colonized in Samaria by the king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=24'>2Ki 17:24</a><br/> Confederate with Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=2'>2Ki 24:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=5'>Jer 39:5</a><br/> The Roman province of, included:<br/> - The land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=3'>Luk 2:3</a> <br/> - Phenicia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=26'>Mar 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=3'>Act 21:3</a> <br/> The fame of Jesus extended over<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=24'>Mat 4:24</a><br/> Paul goes to, with letters to apprehend the Christians; is converted and begins his evangelistic ministry<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=31'>Act 9:31</a><br/><a href='S:Paul'>Paul</a> <br/> Paul preaches in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=41'>Act 15:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=18'>Act 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=3'>Act 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=21'>Gal 1:21</a><br/> Damascus, the capital of<br/> <a href='S:Damascus'>Damascus</a><br/> Wars between, and the kingdoms of Judah and Israel<br/> <a href='S:Israel'>Israel</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=16'>Isa 7:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=7'>Isa 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=17&verse=3'>Isa 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=15'>Jer 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=27'>Jer 49:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=5'>Amo 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=1'>Zec 9:1</a>"}]}